title: Powerslave EX playthrough -- Part 2
description: I really liked the whole medroid-vania feel of this game. Going back and forth between levels with new powerups to get stuff. Really cool. The game was a lot easier than the DOS version though, and I liked the fact that there were usable items in that game. But the weapons in this game were a lot better. Both versions have their merits, but this one is probably a bit better (especially considering you don't have to play in dosbox with pretty bad controls)
